♪We stand tall fearlessly♪

19
00:01:30,860 --> 00:01:35,980
=Fateful Love=

20
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,980
=Episode 25=

21
00:01:51,670 --> 00:01:53,750
Why isn't Prince Xiang coming with us?

22
00:01:55,310 --> 00:01:56,730
He has returned to Xiling
to wait for us.

23
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:01,390
When will our ship arrive?

24
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:03,890
Don't worry. It's coming.

25
00:02:05,490 --> 00:02:07,060
If you need to pass through
Yaoshun Island,

26
00:02:07,380 --> 00:02:09,370
you must get Dongling's approval.

27
00:02:09,900 --> 00:02:11,540
We have to go to Dongling Royal City

28
00:02:11,540 --> 00:02:12,700
to get my mother's consent first.

29
00:02:13,580 --> 00:02:16,060
Crown Prince Xuanyuan,
are you planning to

30
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:17,300
make a move against me in Dongling

31
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,420
and use the opportunity
to rescue Han Ziqing?

32
00:02:20,620 --> 00:02:22,100
Without Dongling's approval,

33
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:23,620
you cannot pass through Yaoshun Island.

34
00:02:24,820 --> 00:02:25,940
But I'm here.

35
00:02:26,900 --> 00:02:28,140
I can represent Dongling.

36
00:02:29,660 --> 00:02:31,430
You're doing this behind Mother's back

37
00:02:32,420 --> 00:02:33,500
and betraying Dongling.

38
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:34,540
You will face retribution.

39
00:02:34,540 --> 00:02:35,380
Don't worry.

40
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:37,820
Regarding borrowing the route
to Consort Yun,

41
00:02:37,820 --> 00:02:39,620
I have already obtained Mother's decree.

42
00:02:39,900 --> 00:02:41,570
I am acting under the decree.

43
00:02:41,980 --> 00:02:42,820
Brother,

44
00:02:42,820 --> 00:02:44,180
you don't need to worry about it.

45
00:02:50,500 --> 00:02:52,380
Brother, it seems your illness
has come back,

46
00:02:53,220 --> 00:02:55,180
you should return to Dongling
for treatment.

47
00:02:58,980 --> 00:02:59,900
Don't stare at me like that.

48
00:03:00,660 --> 00:03:02,460
I'm doing this for your good.

49
00:03:02,460 --> 00:03:04,140
I'm also doing this
so you can get the antidote.

50
00:03:04,140 --> 00:03:05,500
That's why I'm working for them.

51
00:03:08,660 --> 00:03:09,820
You two, stop arguing.

52
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:12,020
Both of you will be credited
once the task is done.

53
00:03:12,660 --> 00:03:14,140
As for who gets the credit,

54
00:03:15,180 --> 00:03:16,020
that's not my concern.

55
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:25,460
Consort Yun, the ship has arrived.

56
00:04:01,980 --> 00:04:02,820
Your Highness.

57
00:04:04,020 --> 00:04:05,090
Your Highness, this way.

58
00:04:41,860 --> 00:04:44,100
Under the nose
of the Tianque Royal Family,

59
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:44,940
someone has built

60
00:04:44,940 --> 00:04:45,980
such a massive secret chamber.

61
00:05:01,140 --> 00:05:01,980
Clear.

62
00:05:02,940 --> 00:05:03,780
Clear.

63
00:05:04,580 --> 00:05:05,420
Clear.

64
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:06,980
Clear.

65
00:05:06,980 --> 00:05:07,940
Beiyue, look.

66
00:05:19,700 --> 00:05:20,580
Yaoshun Island.

67
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:24,580
Could it be that they plan
to take the water route?

68
00:05:26,700 --> 00:05:27,540
Let's go

69
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:28,660
to check the dock.

70
00:05:29,380 --> 00:05:30,220
Yes.

71
00:05:31,060 --> 00:05:35,100
(Xuanyuan)

72
00:05:44,140 --> 00:05:45,460
As an Islander,

73
00:05:46,540 --> 00:05:48,500
you don't deserve to live in this world.

74
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:53,700
You took away Jun Beiyue
and ruined my life.

75
00:05:55,340 --> 00:05:56,180
Han Ziqing,

76
00:05:58,220 --> 00:06:00,100
this is the price you should pay.

77
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:07,220
Enjoy it well.

78
00:06:20,020 --> 00:06:22,140
Princess Zhaoxi,
be careful of your brother.

79
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:23,820
He has deep feelings

80
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:26,220
for Han Ziqing.

81
00:06:27,540 --> 00:06:28,420
As long as I'm here,

82
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:30,100
he won't have a say

83
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:31,820
in Han Ziqing's case.

84
00:06:33,260 --> 00:06:35,140
If you want to clear obstacles,
you must be decisive.

85
00:06:36,140 --> 00:06:37,280
Don't let him cause trouble.

86
00:06:39,780 --> 00:06:41,060
What did she tell you?

87
00:06:41,220 --> 00:06:44,580
Consort Yun said
you have deep feelings for Han Ziqing

88
00:06:44,820 --> 00:06:45,940
and told me to be wary of you.

89
00:06:47,860 --> 00:06:48,700
What are you doing?

90
00:06:49,660 --> 00:06:50,500
What are you doing?

91
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:56,980
From now on,

92
00:06:57,500 --> 00:06:59,650
we will increase the dose of poisons
for Han Ziqing

93
00:07:00,740 --> 00:07:01,770
to torture her

94
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:03,980
and make her life worse than death.

95
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:06,100
No.

96
00:07:07,060 --> 00:07:07,900
Your Highness,

97
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:08,980
they are setting sail.

98
00:07:08,980 --> 00:07:09,820
Trying to escape?

99
00:07:10,780 --> 00:07:12,260
Blow up the bottom of the ship.

100
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:13,620
Don't let anyone escape.

101
00:07:42,460 --> 00:07:43,300
No.

102
00:07:44,420 --> 00:07:45,260
Zhaoxi,

103
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:47,500
Chu Feiyan is deceiving you.

104
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:49,500
She just wants to use Tianque's soldiers
to attack Dongling.

105
00:07:49,500 --> 00:07:50,820
Don't be fooled by her.

106
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:56,100
You should think
about how to save yourself first.

107
00:07:57,020 --> 00:07:58,500
Do you think if something happens to me,

108
00:07:58,500 --> 00:07:59,740
Mother will spare you?

109
00:08:03,180 --> 00:08:04,860
I won't let you die so easily.

110
00:08:06,380 --> 00:08:07,500
Mother is right.

111
00:08:08,980 --> 00:08:10,260
Your value

112
00:08:11,140 --> 00:08:13,620
is to pave the way for me
to become the queen.

113
00:08:20,300 --> 00:08:22,300
At least I have some value.

114
00:08:23,380 --> 00:08:24,220
But you

115
00:08:24,940 --> 00:08:26,900
are worthless.

116
00:08:36,580 --> 00:08:37,420
Your Highness.

117
00:08:38,260 --> 00:08:39,100
Your Highness.

118
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:40,900
Your Highness, there's a situation.

119
00:08:40,900 --> 00:08:41,940
What situation?

120
00:08:41,940 --> 00:08:43,700
A lot of men in black
suddenly appeared on the sea

121
00:08:43,700 --> 00:08:44,900
and started fighting with our people.

122
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:45,740
They are ruthless.

123
00:08:47,340 --> 00:08:49,100
Could it be Jun Beiyue?

124
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:52,180
Quick, set sail.

125
00:08:57,140 --> 00:08:58,180
Release the falcons

126
00:08:58,180 --> 00:08:59,020
and send out the message

127
00:08:59,540 --> 00:09:02,180
that the Fourth Prince of Tianque
is attacking Dongling's ship.

128
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:04,460
- Yes.
- Stop.

129
00:09:04,460 --> 00:09:05,580
Xuanyuan Zhaoxi, stop.

130
00:09:06,140 --> 00:09:07,660
You are no match for Jun Beiyue.

131
00:09:08,220 --> 00:09:10,260
The only solution now
is to release Han Ziqing

132
00:09:10,260 --> 00:09:11,860
and tell him about Chu Feiyan
and Chu Tiange.

133
00:09:11,860 --> 00:09:12,900
There is no other way!

134
00:09:14,500 --> 00:09:16,100
The only solution now

135
00:09:16,100 --> 00:09:17,980
is for both of you to die together.

136
00:09:17,980 --> 00:09:19,260
Xuanyuan Zhaoxi!

137
00:09:19,780 --> 00:09:21,220
Quickly notify Consort Yun.

138
00:09:26,620 --> 00:09:27,460
Ziqing.

139
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:28,460
Ziqing.

140
00:09:30,740 --> 00:09:31,580
Ziqing.

141
00:09:33,820 --> 00:09:34,660
Ziqing, don't be afraid.

142
00:09:36,100 --> 00:09:36,940
Go.

143
00:09:37,660 --> 00:09:38,700
Leave me and go.

144
00:09:40,340 --> 00:09:41,180
Don't be afraid.

145
00:09:41,700 --> 00:09:42,540
I won't go.

146
00:09:53,270 --> 00:09:56,190
♪A fleeting dream, afraid to wake up♪

147
00:09:56,510 --> 00:10:00,190
♪Yet it's a love I never imagined♪

148
