151
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:18,260
♪Turning into a segment of longing♪

152
00:10:19,910 --> 00:10:23,100
♪Your love falls like the night♪

153
00:10:23,890 --> 00:10:26,980
♪The moon and sparse stars illuminate♪

154
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:30,810
♪The emptiness left in me♪

155
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:36,730
♪Light and shadow intertwine,
no time to escape♪

156
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:39,940
Hurry up and go.

157
00:10:42,420 --> 00:10:43,260
Don't be afraid.

158
00:10:44,700 --> 00:10:45,620
Leave me and go.

159
