Hurry up and go.

172
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:35,220
Leave me.

173
00:11:35,220 --> 00:11:36,260
I won't leave you.

174
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:42,540
Ziqing, I won't leave you behind.

175
00:11:44,220 --> 00:11:45,060
- Hurry, go.
- Ziqing.

176
00:11:45,450 --> 00:11:46,300
Go.

177
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:47,740
I won't leave you alone.

178
00:11:49,590 --> 00:11:50,430
Open the door.

179
00:11:50,620 --> 00:11:51,460
Open the door!

180
00:11:52,420 --> 00:11:53,600
Help!

181
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:55,400
Is anyone there?

182
