197
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:35,540
Where is she?

198
00:12:36,700 --> 00:12:37,540
She's dead.

199
00:12:38,380 --> 00:12:39,380
I'm telling you,

200
00:12:39,380 --> 00:12:40,460
if she is dead,

201
00:12:42,380 --> 00:12:44,540
