♪Just to have you by my side♪

216
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,770
♪Still can't forget♪

217
00:13:18,770 --> 00:13:20,380
♪Still hanging on♪

218
00:13:21,940 --> 00:13:22,780
Ziqing.

219
00:13:24,990 --> 00:13:25,830
Ziqing.

220
00:13:27,350 --> 00:13:33,460
♪After all the twists and turns,
you're still here♪

221
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,320
Ziqing.

222
00:13:37,460 --> 00:13:38,300
Ziqing!

223
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:42,060
- Ziqing.
- Come on.

224
00:13:48,680 --> 00:13:50,780
Xuanyuan Lige is still down there.
Hurry and save him.

225
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:53,660
The boat is sinking.
You all go quickly. I'll save him.

226
00:13:53,810 --> 00:13:54,940
Lige!

227
00:13:56,970 --> 00:13:58,740
♪Still can't forget♪

228
00:13:58,740 --> 00:14:00,360
♪Still looking from afar♪

229
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:03,700
♪For love, why fear walking alone♪

