239
00:15:20,100 --> 00:15:21,040
Mother,

240
00:15:21,280 --> 00:15:22,990
why will I die?

241
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:24,860
The crown princes of Dongling

242
00:15:25,820 --> 00:15:27,540
never live past 30.

243
00:15:28,100 --> 00:15:30,060
You must remember your mission

244
00:15:30,060 --> 00:15:31,740
is to assist Zhaoxi

245
00:15:31,740 --> 00:15:32,980
in reviving Dongling.

246
00:15:33,910 --> 00:15:34,780
I can never return

247
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:36,920
to Dongling again.

248
00:15:48,580 --> 00:15:49,510
Don't speak.

249
00:15:49,750 --> 00:15:50,590
It will hurt your spirit.

250
00:16:06,700 --> 00:16:07,890
You did a terrible job.

251
00:16:07,890 --> 00:16:09,430
Don't you feel ashamed to come back?

252
00:16:12,220 --> 00:16:13,340
I didn't expect Jun Beiyue

253
00:16:13,340 --> 00:16:14,780
to catch up so quickly.

254
00:16:14,780 --> 00:16:16,340
Luckily, I escaped in time

255
00:16:16,340 --> 00:16:17,900
and didn't face him directly.

256
00:16:17,900 --> 00:16:19,950
