261
00:16:35,520 --> 00:16:36,360
Forget it.

262
00:16:37,830 --> 00:16:40,400
After all, Jun Beiyue doesn't have
any substantial evidence.

263
00:16:41,540 --> 00:16:43,300
The Sand Worship Ritual
is coming in ten days.

264
00:16:43,540 --> 00:16:45,300
If he dares to provoke us then,

265
00:16:46,190 --> 00:16:47,970
I will have something to say to him.

266
00:16:48,540 --> 00:16:49,580
What do you plan to do?

267
00:16:52,170 --> 00:16:54,210
Han Ziqing has been confirmed

268
00:16:54,210 --> 00:16:55,210
to be an Islander.

269
00:16:56,530 --> 00:16:58,410
If Jun Beiyue remains stubborn

270
00:16:58,410 --> 00:17:00,030
and dares to provoke us,

271
00:17:00,450 --> 00:17:01,810
you should write to the King of Nanzhao

272
00:17:01,820 --> 00:17:03,900
and unite with other countries
to declare war on Tianque.

273
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:05,680
Declare war on Tianque?

274
00:17:05,980 --> 00:17:06,820
What?

275
00:17:07,650 --> 00:17:09,060
