♪May time reach through longing♪

682
00:45:28,080 --> 00:45:33,460
♪To where you are♪

683
00:45:34,250 --> 00:45:40,890
♪No matter how long, I'll never forget♪

684
00:45:41,560 --> 00:45:46,640
♪Crossing the night sky,
with the moon so bright♪

685
00:45:48,200 --> 00:45:54,030
♪May light cut through the darkness
of the night♪

686
00:45:54,380 --> 00:46:00,330
♪To where I found you♪

